javax.accessibility.Accessible, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public final class SearchRecordInternalFrame
extends javax.swing.JInternalFrame

The internal frame enables the user to search for rooms and see search results. In addition it also provides a button panel which launches the booking dialog. It is a singleton.

1.4
